name: Materialistic Tyler Durden Card
description: This is the Materialistic Tyler Durden Card.  We are all chasing that dream that these NFTs are going to make us Happy or Rich someday.  The dream that if we hodl long enough we can see that glimpse of future riches.  The dream that if you have that one single copy of a special artwork close to your heart that no one else will.  Let's not forget that "The things you own end up owning you"-TD.  Here we have a soap tile montage embedded with a portrait of the Great Tyler Durden giving a sense of a "False Mosaic".  Just like the False sense of hope you have that owning this NFT will make you special.  You are not Special.
